               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18470301-name-465" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18470301-name-465" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470301-name-465" type="surname" value="HALLINGAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470301-name-465" type="given" value="SABINA"></interp>SABINA HALLINGAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of James Hallingan, who works at an iron founder's—the prisoner is my son—a little before eight o'clock in the morn<lb></lb>ing, on the 16th Feb., I went out of an errand—I saw the prisoner playing in Exeter-street, Chelsea—I was gone about three-quarters of an hour—when I returned, I missed a pair of child's boots, which I had left in the room—they cost 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
